WEBVTT

00:04.343 --> 00:05.984
The day you die

00:06.727 --> 00:09.626
is just like every other day.

00:12.735 --> 00:17.415
You wake and dress and eat and drink.

00:19.050 --> 00:22.010
Just like every other day.

00:28.533 --> 00:31.384
You don't see death coming.

00:33.000 --> 00:35.040
Or hear its approach.

00:37.000 --> 00:43.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:44.545 --> 00:47.435
Because you are too busy living.

00:53.110 --> 00:56.090
Too busy enjoying your life.

00:58.867 --> 01:01.181
Sating your appetites.

01:39.701 --> 01:41.020
Thank you.

01:41.030 --> 01:45.168
Rich man or beggar,
it does not discriminate.

01:51.846 --> 01:55.610
Death doesn't care about
fleeing your demons,

02:00.492 --> 02:03.492
or making amends for them.

02:15.423 --> 02:18.595
It doesn't care about any of that.

02:19.197 --> 02:23.943
It cares only that this is your time.

02:26.617 --> 02:27.920
Your day...

02:28.857 --> 02:30.050
to die.

02:46.650 --> 02:49.920
And this is the Musketeers' day.

02:59.050 --> 03:01.050
No mistakes this time.

03:05.266 --> 03:06.605
Of course not.

03:07.559 --> 03:08.679
By dusk,

03:09.797 --> 03:11.608
Athos and his friends...

03:13.530 --> 03:15.030
will be dead.

03:41.795 --> 03:44.495
